<h2 class="text-center">
    {% trans -%}
        Which type of access would you like to apply for?
    {%- endtrans %}
</h2>
<div class="row-fluid"><div class="span8 offset2">{% trans %}You currently do not have access to some parts of Investigative Dashboard, because your account has not been verified. In order to get access, please tell us whether you want to be an information requester, or a volunteer researcher.{% endtrans %}</div></div>

<br>

<div class="span12">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span4 offset2 splash-item">
            <h1 class="huge secondary-highlight"><i class="fa fa-question"></i></h1>
            <p class="desc">{% trans %}Information Requester{% endtrans %}</p>
            <p>{% trans %}Take advantage of our database of knowledge to find out more information about companies, individuals, or the relationships between them.{% endtrans %}</p>
            <div class="button-holder">
                <a href="{{ url('request_access_create') }}?access_type=requester" class="btn btn-large">{% trans %}Be a Requester{% endtrans %}</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="span4 splash-item">
            <h1 class="huge secondary-highlight"><i class="fa fa-thumbs-up"></i></h1>
            <p class="desc">{% trans %}Volunteer{% endtrans %}</p>
            <p>{% trans %}We have available public requests that need volunteers. Use your wealth of information to help others find answers.{% endtrans %}</p>
            <div class="button-holder">
                <a href="{{ url('request_access_create') }}?access_type=volunteer" class="btn btn-large">{% trans %}Be a Volunteer{% endtrans %}</a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
